(879, 'Focus Corporation recrute SAP Technical Support Engineers', 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/focus-corporation-recrute-sap-technical-support-engineers/', 'Focus', 'Secteur privé', 'Ariana', '5 jours ago', '19 mai 2021', 'Focus corporation recrute\nSAP Technical Support Engineers\nMission:\nWithin a project team as a Technical Support Engineer, you will support an operator of a SAP client. Your duties will include:\nManaging technical incidents.\nMonitoring and managing the incidents.\nEnsuring quality of services provided on the perimeter of the support incidents.\nDiagnosing and / or resolving technical customer problems level 2 and 3.\nEnsuring preventive maintenance and customer relationship.\nProviding knowledge sharing.\nProfile:\nComputer Engineer.\nFluency in business English is required.\nAble to work effectively in a team environment.\nExcellent written and verbal communication skills.\nExcellent interpersonal skills.\nStrong troubleshooting and problem solving skills.\nFocus on quality delivery.\nAbout Focus Group :\nFocus is a Tunisian Group specialised in software engineering and IT services.\nWith presence in Tunisia and in Europe, Focus offers a wide range of IT solutions in the areas of embedded systems, ERP and BI, IT infrastructure solutions…\nCertified ISO 9001 and CMMI L3, Focus has among its references national and worldwide leaders such as Continental, Nokia-Siemens, Parrot or SAP\nComment postuler :\nPlease Apply Via http://jobs.focus-corporation.com/\nVille : Ariana\nNom / Entreprise : Focus corporation\nEmail : yosra.benabdallah@focus-corporation.com\nTel / Fax : 70 106 100\nAdresse : Focus Building, Z.I Chotrana II, Ariana 2036', 'c#', '2021-05-24 14:16:52');
