(63, 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/softina-recrute-developpeur-confirme-odoo-python/', 'softina recrute développeur confirmé odoo python', 'softinarecrutedéveloppeur confirmé odoo pythonaccompagner mise place gestion odoo analyse besoins installation paramétrage modules odoodéveloppement besoins fonctionnalités système odooprofilune confirmée implémentation modules odoo programmation python solide connaissance python linux javascript css htmlla connaissance dautre erp atout majeurexcellente maîtrise français oral envoyeznous candidature lettre motivation softinarhgmailcomville menzel temime nabeulnom entreprise softinaemail softinarhgmailcomadresse capbon', '7 mois ago', 'python', 'SOFTINA\nrecrute\nDéveloppeur Confirmé Odoo / Python\n-Accompagner nos clients lors de la mise en place des solutions de gestion odoo .\n-Analyse des besoins, Installation, Paramétrage, Formation, …des modules odoo.\n-Développement des besoins et fonctionnalités sous le système odoo.\nProfil:\nUne expérience confirmée en implémentation des modules odoo et programmation Python .\nSolide connaissance en Python , linux , javascript ,CSS , HTML.\nLa connaissance d’autre ERP est un atout majeur.\nExcellente maîtrise du français (oral et écrit)\nComment postuler :\nEnvoyez-nous votre candidature (lettre de motivation et CV) à : softina.rh@gmail.com\nVille : Menzel Temime – Nabeul\nNom / Entreprise : SOFTINA\nEmail : softina.rh@gmail.com\nAdresse : Capbon', 'Softina recrute Développeur Confirmé Odoo / Python'),
(64, 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/looyas-recrute-python-backend-developer-2/', 'looyas recrute python backend developer', 'curious motivated looking challenge looyas fast environment develop boost career python professional willing hard learn lot develop broaden seasoned professional join currently looking passionate engineers seasoned help build product development center european customers ie successful ehealth company new team member rd center tunisia working directly parisian team decide months quickly charge future large set bankable data protection healtcare sdlc looyas equal employer celebrate diversity committed creating inclusive environment employees job descriptionwe looking analytical resultsdriven backend developer team members troubleshoot improve current backend applications processes backend developer use understanding programming languages tools analyze current codes industry developments formulate efficient processes solve problems create seamless users excellent skillsyou team develop healthcare solutionparticipating design implementing productusing iot communicate medical devices backend developer responsibilitiescompile analyze data processes codes troubleshoot problems identify areas improvementcollaborating frontend developers team members establish objectives design functional cohesive codes enhance user experiencedeveloping ideas new programs products features monitoring industry developments trendsrecording data reporting proper parties leadershipparticipating continuing training remain current best practices learn new programming languages better assist team memberstaking lead projects needed backend developer requirementsbachelors degree computer programming computer science related field relevant python andor python django like frameworkfamiliarized jira circleci dockerknowledge documentoriented data base based git filesystem indexation appreciableable delivery services product development sdlcstrong development principlesfrench english verbal organization communications problemsolving people skillspositive outlook strong ethic responsive contacts offer attractive salary package including bonus based performance meals vouchers etccollective insurance medical coverageinternational travelon job traininga modern friendly atmosphere collaboration flexibility respect apply send application hrlooyascom subject job applicationlooyas recruitment python django docker git developer', '10 mois ago', 'python', 'Are you curious, motivated, looking for a challenge? At Looyas, you will have the opportunity to work in a fast adapting environment to develop and boost your career as Python Software Professional\n \nIf you’re willing to work hard, learn a lot, develop your skills and broaden your knowledge while becoming a seasoned Software Professional, join us!\n \nWe are currently looking for passionate engineers (From Junior to Seasoned) to help us build our Product Development Center for our European customers (i.e. a successful e-Health Software Company).\n \nYou’ll become a new team member of our R&D Center in Tunisia and will be working directly with the client’s Parisian Team. And if you decide to do so, within 12/18 months, you’ll quickly become in charge of your future with a large set of very bankable (!) skills (Data protection, Healtcare SDLC; etc)! 🙂\nLooyas is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.\n \nJob description\nWe are looking for an analytical, results-driven Back-end Developer who will work with team members to troubleshoot and improve current back-end applications and processes. The Back-end Developer will use his or her understanding of programming languages and tools to analyze current codes and industry developments, formulate more efficient processes, solve problems, and create a more seamless experience for users. You should have excellent communication and software skills.\n\nYou will be a part of