y you are the right fit for the job.\n\nAnything missing from your application will delay your consideration or cause us to just simply ignore you, sorry 🙁\nCompleted applications should be sent to ikramhomeschool@gmail.com.', 'Home School Tunisia recrute Financial Analyst Intern'),
