(430, 'https://www.keejob.com/offres-emploi/135721/mobile-developer/', 'mobile developer', 'responsibilitieswithin team charge analyzing designing programming maintaining building deploying evolving crossplatform mobile solutionsbeing rd team participate decisionmaking process design cuttingedge mobile applications modern architectures require strong analytical development skillsif responsible passionate committed great enthusiasm grants tech gives develop build solid career dynamic working environmentyour mission technical specification closely working technical business experts teams mobile crossplatform programming flutter implement maintain modern architecture mvvmcross develop best userexperience issues analysis fixing mobile application maintenance improvement perform unitary build delivery deployment packages platforms android ios huaweirequired qualificationssoftware computer science degreetools visual studio android studio github gitscrumdesign patterns programming languages flutter web api mvvm nodejs net core micro services managed services', '20/05/2021', 'android', 'Responsibilities\nWithin an agile team, you will be in charge of analyzing, designing,\r\nprogramming, maintaining, building, deploying and evolving cross-platform\r\nmobile solutions.\nBeing part of the R&D team, you will participate in the\r\ndecision-making process to design cutting-edge mobile applications with modern\r\ntechnologies and architectures which require strong analytical and development\r\nskills\nIf you have an experience between 1 and 3 years, you are responsible,\r\npassionate, committed and work with great enthusiasm, Grant’s Tech gives you\r\nthe opportunity to develop skills and build a solid career in a dynamic working\r\nenvironment.\nYour mission\n- Write technical specification while closely working with the technical\r\nand business experts’ teams.\n- Mobile cross-platform programming under Flutter.\n- Implement and maintain modern architecture such as MVVM-cross \