(64, 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/looyas-recrute-python-backend-developer-2/', 'Looyas recrute Python backend developer', 'Are you curious, motivated, looking for a challenge? At Looyas, you will have the opportunity to work in a fast adapting environment to develop and boost your career as Python Software Professional\n \nIf you’re willing to work hard, learn a lot, develop your skills and broaden your knowledge while becoming a seasoned Software Professional, join us!\n \nWe are currently looking for passionate engineers (From Junior to Seasoned) to help us build our Product Development Center for our European customers (i.e. a successful e-Health Software Company).\n \nYou’ll become a new team member of our R&D Center in Tunisia and will be working directly with the client’s Parisian Team. And if you decide to do so, within 12/18 months, you’ll quickly become in charge of your future with a large set of very bankable (!) skills (Data protection, Healtcare SDLC; etc)! 🙂\nLooyas is an equal opportunity employer. We celebrate diversity and are committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.\n \nJob description\nWe are looking for an analytical, results-driven Back-end Developer who will work with team members to troubleshoot and improve current back-end applications and processes. The Back-end Developer will use his or her understanding of programming languages and tools to analyze current codes and industry developments, formulate more efficient processes, solve problems, and create a more seamless experience for users. You should have excellent communication and software skills.\n\nYou will be a part of a team that develop a healthcare solution\nParticipating in design and implementing software product\nUsing IoT technologies to communicate with medical devices\n\n \nBack-end Developer Responsibilities:\n\nCompile and analyze data, processes, and codes to troubleshoot problems and identify areas for improvement.\nCollaborating with the front-end developers and other team members to establish objectives and design more functional, cohesive codes to enhance the user experience.\nDeveloping ideas for new programs, products, or features by monitoring industry developments and trends.\nRecording data and reporting it to proper parties, such as clients or leadership.\nParticipating in continuing education and training to remain current on best practices, learn new programming languages, and better assist other team members.\nTaking lead on projects, as needed.\n\n \nBack-end Developer Requirements:\n\nBachelor’s degree in computer programming, computer science, or a related field.\n4 years of relevant experience with python 2.7 and/or python 3, Django like Framework.Familiarized with Jira/ CircleCI / Docker\nKnowledge about document-oriented data base, based on git (filesystem) and xapian (indexation) is very appreciable.\nAble to delivery services using a product development SDLC\nStrong Knowledge of Agile development principles\nFrench, English verbal and written\nSkills in organization, communications, problem-solving and people skills\nPositive outlook, strong work ethic, and responsive to clients and contacts\n\n \nWhat we offer you\n\nAn attractive salary package, including bonus based on performance, meals vouchers, etc.\nCollective insurance for medical coverage\nInternational travel\nOn the job training\nA modern workspace with a friendly atmosphere, collaboration, flexibility and respect.\n\n \nTo apply, please send your application to: hr@looyas.com with the subject “LSP0720 job application\n#looyas #recruitment #python #Django #Docker #git #developer', '10 mois ago', NULL),
(65, 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/slnee-tunisie-recrute-developpeur-full-stack-python/', 'Slnee Tunisie recrute Développeur Full Stack python', 'Slnee Tunisie recrute\nDéveloppeur Full Stack python\nMission:\n• Etudier et définir, conjointement avec le responsable applicatif, la conception technique des développements à réaliser\n• Développer les fonctionnalités en Python le cas échéant, systématiser les tests unitaires\n• Mettre en place et réaliser des tests d’intégration (2à2, bout en bout)\n• Entretenir le patrimoine documentaire (spécifications, plans de tests)\nProfil:\nDéveloppeuse/eur logiciel depuis 3 années, de formation BAC+5 et passionné(e) par la programmation\nMaîtrise\n• Python 2.7 et 3.5\n• framework : DJANGO/ FLASK/FRAPPE,\n• Base de données : MariaDB, Mysql,\n• HTML5, BootStrap,\n• Javascript : Jquery et Node JS,\nConnaissances\n– Git, Jenkins SONAR, les principes ORM\n– Avoir des connaissances sur l’erp Odoo est un atout\nAvantage\n– Environnement de travail agréable et convivial.\nLangue\n– Arabe et Anglais.\nNationalité\n– Tunisienne.\nLieu de travail\n– Tunisie.\nComment postuler :\nEnvoyer votre CV à l’adresse : career@slnee.com\nVille : Ariana\nNom / Entreprise : Slnee Tunisie\nEmail : career@slnee.com\nTel / Fax : 71702402\nAdresse : Ariana', '11 mois ago', NULL),
