(163, 'https://www.farojob.net/jobs/inttime-by-machinestalk-recrute-senior-java-jee-developer/', 'Int:Time by machinestalk recrute Senior Java Jee Developer', 'Int:Time by machinestalk recrute\nSenior Java Jee Developer\nWho we are :\n– Be a part of a growing team of talented people responsible for developing products in the IoT domain based on advanced technologies (Big Data, Microservices, Spring, Angular, …).\n– Share responsibility for creating and influencing innovative solutions that meet not only functional but also performance, scalability and reliability requirements.\n– Work in an agile environment with skilled developers, DevOps and QA engineers and architects on developing world class products.\nWhat Do we offer :\nEngineer in Computer Science or related field with rich experience in JEE, Spring Framework, and Microservices architecture.\nWe love it when it feels like home. We start the day right with fresh breakfast, we play table ping pong, we create clubs and enjoy doing activities, and together we win football tournaments and go to the gym.\nMinimum working experience of 3 years in Java/JEE,\nExperience with Spring Boot and Microservices architecture\nIntellectual curiosity, positive attitude, and you enjoy collaborating with a team\nComment postuler :\nSend your updated CV in French or English to carreertunisia@Machinestalk.com and include the job title in the subject line.\nVille : tunis\nNom / Entreprise : IN:TIME by machinestalk\nEmail : ghada.grami@machinestalk.com\nTel / Fax : 24898467\nAdresse : 6 Rue Taimour, Tunis, Tunisie', '2 ans ago', NULL),
