(327, 'Conecta Tunisie recute Magasinier', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/conecta-tunisie-recute-magasinier-101875/', 'Tunis', 'CONECTA-TUNISIE recrute Magasinier Tâches et opérations 1/Assurer la réception et le déchargement des import : Effectuer le déchargement des matières premières . Manipuler et ranger les matières premières 2/ Stockage…', '02 avril 2021            ', 'Tâches et opérations 1/Assurer la réception et le déchargement des import : Effectuer le déchargement des matières premières . Manipuler et ranger les matières premières 2/ Stockage du MP 3/ Assurer le chargement des exports :Emballer les produits finis. ; :Préparation des exports selon les procédures prédéfinies ; Chargement de produit Fini 4/ Préparer les ordres de fabrication: Préparer les matières premières et les composants nécessaires; Transmettre les ordres de fabrication au service de production ; Alimenter les lignes de production par la MP selon les procédures prédéfinies 5/ Gérer des stocks :Etiqueter et classer des produits. Ranger des produits ;:Tenir des stocks et contrôler la rotation.; Tenir une gestion de stocks assistés par Ordinateur ; :Participer aux travaux d’inventaire 6/ Utiliser de matériels de manutention :Déplacer et manutentionner des marchandises et des colis; Habilité au conduite du chariot élévateur ; transpalette et autres', 'Compétences requises pour l’exercice du métier: • Réceptionner et stocker les produits. • Reconnaître et Vérifier les produits. • Préparer les livraisons et les expéditions. • Conduire et piloter en sécurité d’un chariot automoteur de manutention • Réaliser des inventaires • Règles et consignes de sécurité • Modalité de stockage • Gestes et postures de manutention • Respecter les délais (préparation des livraisons et des tournées d’expédition). • Respecter des processus de contrôle rigoureux (réception des produits, décompte des quantités prélevées sur le ..). • Respecter les règles d’hygiène et de sécurité • Savoir manipuler l’outil informatique Savoir-être professionnels :', 'Ce poste exige différentes qualités : 1) la rigueur avec une parfaite concentration. 2) Avoir la bonne organisation et se montrer consciencieux 3) Réactivité, sens de l’organisation, rigueur, Autonome Permis de conduire obligatoire', 'Nom / Entreprise : CONECTA-TUNISIE Email : a.karoui@lorenzgroup.com Tel : 72290149 Fax : 72290863 Adresse : ROUTE DE MENZEL BOUZELFA KM 1', 'Signaler cette annonce', '', 'NULL', 'react', '2021-05-24 14:08:37'),
(340, 'Creativ-Ceutical is looking for Prma Analyst', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/conseil-consulting/creativ-ceutical-is-looking-for-prma-analyst-102458/', 'Tunis', 'Creativ-Ceutical is looking for PRMA Analyst The Opportunity The employee is expected to support the realisation of pricing, reimbursement and market access (PRMA) projects for clients across multiple therapeutic and…', '12 mai 2021            ', 'The Opportunity The employee is expected to support the realisation of pricing, reimbursement and market access (PRMA) projects for clients across multiple therapeutic and geographic markets. Amongst the tasks and responsibilities will be to: • • Data gathering via secondary research and data analysis in support of client projects; • • Aiding design and development of systematic review protocols and carry out the study selection (screening) and data extraction • • Provide background research/data for proposals, projects and/or internal projects; • • Perform quantitative analyses to aid development of recommendations. Secondary research example: An Analyst may be asked to look up, analyze, and graphically represent data regarding the launch price, sales volume and coverage and reimbursement status for a set of products similar to our client’s product in order to refine key forecasting or valuation model assumptions and inputs.', 'The Requirements This position requires a Pharmacist degree or Medical Doctor degree or PhD/MSc/Engineer degree in Biology and an interest in public health, health economics, epidemiology and statistics. • Analytical and interpretative skills; • Well-developed communication skills, including presentations and report writing; • Ability to adapt, work in a team and independently; • Flexibility and ability to cope with pressure and challenges; • Attention to detail and ability to deliver high quality work within timeline; • Keenness to learn and commitment to a rapid development curve; • Strong interpersonal and relationship building skills; • Excellent IT literacy e.g. Word, PowerPoint and Excel; • English skills (both oral and written). • A second language is desired.', 'We Offer • Salary based on your experience and skills. • Participation in interesting and challenging projects in global structures. • Multicultural, dynamic environment. • Good working atmosphere. • Opportunity to build up expertise in quality assurance through coaching and trainings. • Work in a well-established and international company.', 'Comment postuler : If you are looking to develop expertise in scientific consulting, in a young and dynamic environment, please send your CV and a cover letter explaining your motivations at: careers@creativ-ceutical.com. Applications will only be accepted in English.', 'Ville : Tunis Nom / Entreprise : Creativ-ceutical Email : careers@creativ-ceutical.com Tel / Fax : 70 294 985 Adresse : Rue du Lac Ghar El Melh, Immeuble Elysée 2 ème étage Les Berges du Lac 1053 Tunisia', '', '', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21'),
(341, 'Creativ-Ceutical is looking for SLR Analyst', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/conseil-consulting/creativ-ceutical-is-looking-for-slr-analyst-102455/', 'Tunis', 'Creativ-ceutical is looking for SLR Analyst The Opportunity The employee is expected to participate in Health Economics and Outcomes Research (HEOR) projects for clients across multiple therapeutic and geographic markets….', '12 mai 2021            ', 'The Opportunity The employee is expected to participate in Health Economics and Outcomes Research (HEOR) projects for clients across multiple therapeutic and geographic markets. You will be working in the evidence synthesis team, on systematic literature reviews relating to clinical, health economic and outcomes research studies. You will be involved at all the steps of the projects; your tasks and responsibilities will include: • Development strategies for literature reviews (search strategies, protocol report) • Carry out the study selection (screening) • Data extraction • Critical appraisal of clinical, health economic and outcomes research studies • Writing the review reports and develop slide kit • Participate in internal initiatives e.g. attend or prepare internal presentations on relevant topics', 'The Requirements • Master in public health, biology, pharmacy or other life sciences. Postgraduate degree in the field would be an asset; • Good communication skills, including presentations and report writing; • Good knowledge in Microsoft Office e.g. Word, PowerPoint and Excel; • Ability to synthetize complex information; • Good attention to detail and ability to meet high quality standards; • Ability to adapt, work in a team and independently;', 'Comment postuler : If you are looking to develop expertise in scientific consulting, in a young and dynamic environment, please send your CV and a cover letter explaining your motivations at: careers@creativ-ceutical.com Applications will only be accepted in English.', 'Ville : Tunis Nom / Entreprise : Creativ-ceutical Email : careers@creativ-ceutical.com Tel / Fax : 70 294 985 Adresse : Rue du Lac Ghar El Melh, Immeuble Elysée 2 ème étage Les Berges du Lac 1053 Tunisia', '', '', 'Signaler cette annonce', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21'),
(342, 'Chargé.e de suivi, évaluation et rapportage – PNUD', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/informatique-telecom-internet/charge-e-de-suivi-evaluation-et-rapportage-pnud-102403/', 'Ben Arous', 'Détails de l\'opportunité Régions concernées par cette opportunité: Tunisie                       Background UNDP is committed to achieving workforce diversity in terms…', '07 mai 2021            ', 'Signaler cette annonce', '', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'NULL', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21'),
(344, 'Home School is looking for Financial Analyst Intern', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/comptabilite-finance-statistiques/home-school-is-looking-for-financial-analyst-intern-102105/', 'Tunis', 'Home School is looking for Financial Analyst Intern YOU: – Have a good understanding of finance and investment and an analytical mind who can look at the same problem from…', '18 avril 2021            ', 'YOU: – Have a good understanding of finance and investment and an analytical mind who can look at the same problem from different angles, accurately examine data, and draw logical conclusions. – LOVE looking at numbers, analyzing numbers, and transforming numbers into a **SEXY DOCUMENT THAT ATTRACT THE MOST STUBBORN INVESTORS.** – Embrace uncertainty and go with the flow. – Are professional and take your work seriously. – Are MOTIVATED to learn, grow, and take on any challenges.', 'MUST HAVES: – Background in finance, preferably a student of TBS, ISG, ESSECT, IHEC, etc.. – Mastery of Google sheet and presentation tools. – A knack for logical thinking and details. – Great Communicator! English! All of our communication will happen in English. – Well-versed and understood in the start-up and investment scene in Tunisia and internationally. – You’re cool, chill, and open-minded, with the ability to take direction and work on a team. – Living in Tunis, preferably close to our Belvedére office (let us know if you are close) – Good French.', 'Duties / Responsibilities: – Analyze current and past financial data and performance. – Prepare financial studies based on those analyses. – Explore investment opportunities. – Prepare presentations for investors. – Support the team to apply for funds/grants, etc..when needed.', 'To apply, Your Email MUST have: – A CV – Available times for an interview – A small introduction of yourself and why you are the right fit for the job. Anything missing from your application will delay your consideration or cause us to just simply ignore you, sorry ? Completed applications should be sent to ikramhomeschool@gmail.com', 'Comment postuler : Completed applications should be sent to ikramhomeschool@gmail.com', 'Ville : Tunis Nom / Entreprise : Home School Email : ikramhomeschool@gmail.com Tel / Fax : 00216 93134618 Adresse : 22 Avenue Des Etats Unis, Tunis, Tunisia 1002', 'Signaler cette annonce', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21'),
(347, 'Home School Tunisia recrute Financial Analyst Intern', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/offres-emploi/comptabilite-finance-statistiques/home-school-tunisia-recrute-financial-analyst-intern-101958/', 'Tunis', 'Home School is looking for a Financial Analyst Intern. You will be joining a team of two to collaborate on raising funds and exploring investment opportunities. This position is more…', '09 avril 2021            ', 'Have a good understanding of finance and investment and an analytical mind who can look at the same problem from different angles, accurately examine data, and draw logical conclusions. LOVE looking at numbers, analyzing numbers, and transforming numbers into a SEXY DOCUMENT THAT ATTRACT THE MOST STUBBORN INVESTORS. Embrace uncertainty and go with the flow. Are professional and take your work seriously. Are MOTIVATED to learn, grow, and take on any challenges.', 'MUST HAVES:', 'Background in finance, preferably a student of TBS, ISG, ESSECT, IHEC, etc.. Mastery of Google sheet and presentation tools. A knack for logical thinking and details. Great Communicator! English! All of our communication will happen in English. Well-versed and understood in the start-up and investment scene in Tunisia and internationally. You’re cool, chill, and open-minded, with the ability to take direction and work on a team. Living in Tunis, preferably close to our Belvedére office (let us know if you are close) Good French.', 'Duties / Responsibilities:', 'Analyze current and past financial data and performance. Prepare financial studies based on those analyses. Explore investment opportunities. Prepare presentations for investors. Support the team to apply for funds/grants, etc..when needed.', 'ABOUT US:', 'At Home School, we are passionate about helping improve the spoken English standards in the country.', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21'),
(348, 'Focus Corporation is looking for Process & Tools Analyst', 'https://www.offre-emploi.tn/immigration-bourses/focus-corporation-is-looking-for-process-tools-analyst-101896/', 'Tunis', 'Focus Corporation recrute Process & Tools Analyst Mission – Act as tools administrator (access management, management enablement and support, tool maintenance, data quality & integrity…) – Maintain systems integrations to…', '03 avril 2021            ', 'Mission – Act as tools administrator (access management, management enablement and support, tool maintenance, data quality & integrity…) – Maintain systems integrations to promote best practices and seamless processes – Actively troubleshoot issues within our tools and coordinate with different stakeholders to ensure timely resolution – Work with end-users to provide best practices and tips on tool usage including training, documentation, and support as necessary – Develop a solid understanding of the department-specific business processes and work with the business to design and implement new processes. Model and implement business processes as data structures. – Collect business needs and write functionnal/technical specifications – Continuously evolve existing processes & tools – Stay current with tool releases and corresponding documentation and provide new functionalities and solutions as needed. – Conduct comparative studies, benchmarks and tests necessary for the choice of tools and solutions in line with needs. – Identify optimal solutions in terms of quality / cost – Assist the IT team in setting up and deploying solutions', 'Profile: Bachelor/Master’s degree in Business-oriented Computing Work experience with application and software development and/or administration Ability to problem solve high-level software and application issues Logical thinking and Problem solving Very good communication skills Good reporting', 'Comment postuler : Send your CVs to : rh@focus-corporation.com and recruit@focus-corporation.com and yosra.benabdallah@focus-corporation.com', 'Ville : lac 2 Nom / Entreprise : FOCUS TECHNOLOGY SOLUTIONS Email : yosra.benabdallah@focus-corporation.com Tel / Fax : 70 106 100 Adresse : IMM WAFA AV DE LA BOURSE 1 ER ETAGE BUREAU B1 LAC 2 LES BERGES DU LAC 1053 Tunis Site Web : http://www.focus-corporation.com/', 'About Focus Group : Focus is a Tunisian Group specialised in software engineering and IT services. With presence in Tunisia and in Europe, Focus offers a wide range of IT solutions in the areas of embedded systems, ERP and BI, IT infrastructure solutions, Cloud … Certified ISO 9001 and CMMI L3, Focus has among its references national and worldwide leaders.', 'Signaler cette annonce', '', 'analyst', '2021-05-24 14:09:21');
