(289, 'ntersos Humanitarian Aid Organization recrute Global Supply Officer', 'https://www.tunisietravail.net/ntersos-humanitarian-aid-organization-recrute-global-supply-officer-94282/', 'INTERSOS recrute Global Supply Officer (National Position) INTERSOS is an independent humanitarian organization that assists the victims of natural disasters, armed conflicts and exclusion. Its activities are based on the principles of solidarity, justice, human dignity, ', 'Mai, 2021', 'INTERSOS is an independent humanitarian organization that assists the victims of natural disasters, armed conflicts and exclusion. Its activities are based on the principles of solidarity, justice, human dignity, equality of rights and opportunities, respect for diversity and coexistence, paying special attention to the most vulnerable people.\nTerms of reference\nJob Title: Global Supply Officer (National position)\nCode: SR-00-1822\nDuty station: Tunis, Tunisia\nStarting date: June 2021\nContract duration: 12 months\nReporting to: Area Logistics Coordinator\nSalary and contract: fix-term contract, around 3000/3200 TND net/month', 'General context of the project\nINTERSOS is a humanitarian organization that works all over the world bringing assistance to people in danger victims of natural disasters and armed conflicts. It provides first aid, food, shelter, medical assistance and basic goods. It ensures that basic needs, as education, clean water and health, are met.\nManaging effectively an agile Supply-Chain guarantees that our missions are well equipped to deliver the required assistance and that all goods and services meet the highest quality specifications.\nWe are currently looking for a motivated and solution orientated Global Supply Officer to join INTERSOS Logistics Department where it will be involved with the daily Supply-Chain management of our 19 missions across the world.', 'General purpose of the position\nBased in INTERSOS Tunisian Hub, and under the Supervision of the HQ Supply Coordinator, the Global Supply Officer will provide operational support to all INTERSOS’s missions/projects with focus on Procurement, Order Managem', 'International sourcing and procurement\no Source and procure of medical supplies, IT and communication equipment, visibility items, among others.\no Create and manage the INTERSOS’s Global Supply Catalogue\no Support the preparation, launch and evaluation of', 'International order management and freight transportation\no Manage the international order pipeline, acting as the focal point for all missions.\no Support missions to prepare Purchase Requests and BoQ’s.\no Follow up orders placed to Humanitarian Procureme', 'c#', '2021-05-24 14:08:39'),
